      "url": "https://api.github.com/users/flawlesscode254",
      "html_url": "https://github.com/flawlesscode254",
      "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/flawlesscode254/followers",
      "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/flawlesscode254/following%7B/other_user%7D",
      "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/flawlesscode254/gists%7B/gist_id%7D",
      "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/flawlesscode254/starred%7B/owner%7D%7B/repo%7D",
      "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/flawlesscode254/subscriptions",
      "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/flawlesscode254/orgs",
      "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/flawlesscode254/repos",
      "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/flawlesscode254/events%7B/privacy%7D",
      "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/flawlesscode254/received_events",
      "type": "User",
      "site_admin": false,
      "name": null,
      "patch_url": null
    },
    "body": "When block.vtx is empty, `block.vtx.size() - 1` causes integer underflow \r\nsince size() returns size_t (unsigned) and subtracting 1 wraps around \r\nto a large number. This fix adds an explicit cast to int to prevent \r\nthe underflow.\r\nFixes a potential crash when processing blocks with zero transactions.",
    "labels": [],
    "created_at": "2026-04-12T04:09:21Z",
